 "768312218730772", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031436_768312222064105_2483983745682146754_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=53KKqsP-GxoQ7kNvgHomIJr&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA8YpM4rLHr6biqB7uGETmO84K-74vMQ_CZ1VDCgo8_ng&oe=66D3191E"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240210-1504414_2.png", "id": "1144388200046417", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003227_1144388210046416_8982093088097178928_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qnu6iL85QS0Q7kNvgEgwG83&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBYE6l6zBgFuIcTwlx7nnKJviy-AyBRtcvFAkyba6-UGw&oe=66D2F211"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240210-115437.png", "id": "1405118490144295", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75230048_1405118493477628_4689660376237645316_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=o_M6XestEMYQ7kNvgG6CQ99&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC515tqgrBoqZJyRHEMrgVb2CH1IQnm2C8suYFMP9d4fw&oe=66D3021B"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240209-2137122.png", "id": "7621650634553270", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75556799_7621650644553269_1655627145384024300_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bhU408Sn2kIQ7kNvgFmpVJD&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAZRbi_P4YUJARnoyoxk81jK6Eh2WktS8IxUb6cOet2EA&oe=66D2F81D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Project_Y: Working Title", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This game is the Japanese version.\nIt supports Japanese only.\n\n\"A true ghost story told by a person named Y.\nIt was about an investigation to find out the true meaning of a common self-inflicted urban legend that says, ``If you hear it, you'll be cursed.''\nand...\nThere is a ``sinister existence'' that appears and disappears there.\nThis project reconstructed those interview records as 360\u00b0 videos and produced and developed them as interactive content using live-action VR.\n\n\n- It comes with \"\